[SN]TITLE[SN]
Valentine's tips from Lancashire lovebirds who met as children

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A couple who first met as children have shared their Valentine's Day relationship tips after more than seven decades of marriage.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
14 February 2017 Last updated at 17:00 GMT
Thomas Howard and his wife Irene, now aged in their 90s, first met as children living on the same Lancashire street in 1931, and married after World War Two.
